casebody.data:
No. 11-5810. In re Mark C. Jackson, Petitioner. 565 U.S. 941, 132 S. Ct. 419,

181 L. Ed. 2d 290,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7195. October 11, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of mandamus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Justice Kagan *291took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
